      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a sharp, responsive power band. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the chassis has undergone rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate fatigue, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term engine health. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this platform is renowned for. This is a mechanically sound specimen optimized for peak lateral acceleration and analog engagement.",
